                      🪵 Step 1: The Wood
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-amber-800">
                      We begin with seasoned mahogany and maple, hand-selected for resonance.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Step 2 -->
