                      🔨 Step 2: The Carve
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-amber-800">
                      Each piece is shaped by master hands — not machines.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Step 3 -->
            <div class="journey-step flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-4 sm:gap-6 md:gap-8 py-8 sm:py-12 md:py-16 opacity-0 transform translate-y-10 transition-all duration-700">
                <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
                    <img src="/images/assembly.jpg" 
                         alt="Assembly Process" 
                         class="rounded-lg shadow-xl w-full h-48 sm:h-64 md:h-80 lg:h-auto object-cover">
                </div>
                <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 text-center lg:text-left px-2 sm:px-4">
                    <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-2 sm:mb-4 text-amber-900">
                      🧩 Step 3: Assembly
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-amber-800">
                      Bringing together every detail, like fitting the soul into the body.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Step 4 -->
            <div class="journey-step flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-4 sm:gap-6 md:gap-8 py-8 sm:py-12 md:py-16 opacity-0 transform translate-y-10 transition-all duration-700">
